<context>
Here is a list of all character attributes:
{% for attrName, attrDef in attributeDefinitions %}- {{ attrName }}: {{ attrDef.description }}
{% endfor %}

Here is a list of available equipment slot types:
{% for slot in gearSlots %}- {{ slot }}
{% endfor %}

<character>
<name>{{ character.name }}</name>
<role>{{ character.role }}</role>
<description>{{ character.description }}</description>
<class>{{ character.class }}</class>
<level>{{ character.level }}</level>
<race>{{ character.race }}</race>
</character>
</context>

{% if lorebookEntries and lorebookEntries.length > 0 %}
<worldLore>
{% for entry in lorebookEntries %}
<loreEntry>{{ entry.content }}</loreEntry>
{% endfor %}
</worldLore>
{% endif %}

I'd like you to generate a set of 1 to 5 items that would be found in the above character's inventory in the above setting. The items should be appropriate for the setting and the character's role within it.{% if lorebookEntries and lorebookEntries.length > 0 %} Incorporate relevant elements from the world lore provided above.{% endif %} Output them in the format below:

<items>
{% include "_includes/item.njk" %}
[0-4 more items depending on how many you generate]
</items>

